(88, 1, 66, 'Post', 'body', '<ol>\n	<li>\n		<span style="background-color: transparent; ">Verificar quais tens&otilde;es nos pinos 11 e 12 no soquete P2 na fonte, deve ser aproximadamente conforme abaixo:</span><br />\n		<p style="background-color: transparent; ">\n			<span style="background-color: transparent; ">pino 11 -&gt; 3,3V.</span></p>\n		<p style="background-color: transparent; ">\n			<span style="background-color: transparent; "><span style="background-color: transparent; ">pino 12 -&gt; 4,8V.</span></span></p>\n	</li>\n	<li>\n		<span style="background-color: transparent; ">â€‹</span>Estando correto as tens&otilde;es do BL_ON e DIM a falha esta na fonte, n&atilde;o tendo as tens&otilde;es acima realizar o procedimento abaixo conforme imagem.</li>\n</ol>\n<ul>\n	<li style="background-color: transparent; ">\n		<span style="background-color: transparent; ">Soltar o cabo de alimenta&ccedil;&atilde;o da SSB no soquete P802, ligar os pinos 7,10,11 e 12 e ligar a TV as l&acirc;mpadas devem acender e tamb&eacute;m ter as tens&otilde;es de 24V, procedendo desta maneira atribuir a falha de n&atilde;o acender as l&acirc;mpadas ao painel SSB.</span></li>\n</ul>\n<div style="background-color: transparent; ">\n	&nbsp;</div>\n<div style="background-color: transparent; ">\n	Clique na imagem para ampliar</div>\n<div style="background-color: transparent; ">\n	&nbsp;</div>\n<div style="background-color: transparent; ">\n	<a href="/ckfinder/userfiles/images/teste lampadas.jpg"><img alt="" src="/ckfinder/userfiles/images/teste%20lampadas.jpg" style="border-top-width: 1px; border-right-width: 1px; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-left-width: 1px; border-top-style: solid; border-right-style: solid; border-bottom-style: solid; border-left-style: solid; float: left; width: 214px; height: 160px; " /></a></div>\n<p>\n	&nbsp;</p>', '<ol>\r\n	<li>\r\n		<span style="background-color: transparent; ">Verificar quais tens&otilde;es nos pinos 11 e 12 no soquete P2 na fonte, deve ser aproxi