(135, 13, 'Reparo Fonte de AlimentaÃ§Ã£o.', '<ul>\n	<li>\n		Para reparo na fonte de alimenta&ccedil;&atilde;o verificar a circular AG11-017,&nbsp;verificar os componentes dispon&iacute;veis para reparo, conforme lista abaixo.</li>\n	<li>\n		Fazer o pedido da pe&ccedil;a necess&aacute;ria, n&atilde;o tendo o componente necess&aacute;rio na lista abaixo ou mercado paralelo, ent&atilde;o enviar a fonte para conserto no CRP.</li>\n	<li>\n		Para enviar a placa para o CRP, dever&aacute; ser inserido o c&oacute;digo original da mesma no sistema GVS.</li>\n</ul>\n<p style="margin-left: 40px; ">\n	<strong>C&oacute;digo da Fonte de alimenta&ccedil;&atilde;o.</strong></p>\n<table border="1" cellpadding="1" cellspacing="1" class="tabela" style="width: 500px; ">\n	<tbody>\n		<tr>\n			<td>\n				<p style="margin-left: 40px; ">\n					<strong><span style="color:#000000;">PAINEL EL&Eacute;TRICO FONTE IPB 40 PLHE_P986A B</span></strong></p>\n			</td>\n			<td>\n				<p style="margin-left: 40px; ">\n					<strong><span style="color:#000000;">2722 171 90105</span></strong></p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n	</tbody>\n</table>\n<p style="margin-left: 40px; ">\n	&nbsp;</p>\n<p style="margin-left: 40px; ">\n	<strong>C&oacute;digo e Localiza&ccedil;&atilde;o de Componentes.</strong></p>\n<table border="1" cellpadding="1" cellspacing="1" class="tabela" style="width: 500px; ">\n	<tbody>\n		<tr>\n			<td>\n				<span style="color:#000000;"><strong>D210</strong></span></td>\n			<td>\n				<span style="color:#000000;"><strong>DIODO - SB3200</strong></span></td>\n			<td>\n				<span style="color:#000000;"><strong>9965 100 43937</strong></span></td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td>\n				<span style="color:#000000;"><strong>D510</strong></span></td>\n			<td>\n				<span style="color:#000000;"><strong>DIODO - UF4007</strong></span></td>\n			<td>\n				<span style="color:#000000;"><strong>9965 100 43938</strong></span></td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td>\n				<span style="color:#000000;"><strong>Q501</strong></span></td>\n			<td>\