(219, 13, 'Teste das lÃ¢mpadas e identificar a falha se SSB ou Fonte.', '<ul>\n	<li>\n		Para este caso verificar as tens&otilde;es de alimenta&ccedil;&atilde;o do painel inversor (24V) e tens&atilde;o de referencia BL_ON_OFF, verificar imagem abaixo:</li>\n</ul>\n<p>\n	Clique na imagem para ampliar</p>\n<p>\n	<a href="/ckfinder/userfiles/images/Sem imagem teste inversor.jpg"><img alt="" src="/ckfinder/userfiles/images/Sem imagem teste inversor.jpg" style="float: left; width: 200px; height: 150px; " /></a></p>', 663, 75, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(220, 13, 'Options Bytes e Display code.', '<ul>\n	<li>\n		Para acessar o Modo SAM (Service) digitar a sequ&ecirc;ncia abaixo com o Controle Remoto original - 062596 Info ou OSD.</li>\n	<li>\n		Para alterar o Display code se necess&aacute;rio, digitar 062598 Menu e o n&uacute;mero referente ao display conforme tabela abaixo:</li>\n	<li>\n		Funcionando a sequencia a TV devera ir para stand-by.</li>\n</ul>\n<table border="1" cellpadding="1" cellspacing="1" class="tabela" style="width: 500px; ">\n	<tbody>\n		<tr>\n			<td>\n				<span style="color:#000000;"><strong>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;MODELO</strong></span></td>\n			<td>\n				<span style="color:#000000;"><strong>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; OPTION BYTE</strong></span></td>\n			<td>\n				<span style="color:#000000;"><strong>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Display Code - Display<br />\n				&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; LC320WXN-SAB1</strong></span></td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td>\n				<span style="color:#000000;"><strong>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;32PFL3403/78</strong></span></td>\n			<td>\n				<div>\n					<span style="color:#000000;"><strong>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; OB1-000 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;OB5-008<br />\n					&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; OB2-029 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;OB6-233<br />\n					&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; OB3-148 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;OB7-132<br />\n					&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; OB4-253 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</strong></span></div>\n			</td>\n			<td>\n				<span style="color:#000000;"><strong>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 136</strong></span></td>\n		</tr>\n	</tbody>\n</table>\n<p>\n	&nbsp;</p>', 663, 12, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(221, 13, 'Indica a letra F ou Cf e nÃ£o atua comandos.', '<ul>\n	<li>\n		Para este caso ligar o produto e pressionar as teclas <strong><span style="color:#000000;">(Volume - e Programa - ) </span></strong>simultaneamente por 5 segundos.</li>\n</ul>', 663, 23, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(222, 13, 'Cliente reclama da qualidade da imagem.', '<ul>\n	<li>\n		Para este caso verificar qual tipo de sinal est&aacute; sendo enviado para a TV.</li>\n	<li>\n		Para ter uma &oacute;tima transmiss&atilde;o de imagem para TV &eacute; recomend&aacute;vel uma sinal de alta defini&ccedil;&atilde;o, conectados via HDMI atrav&eacute;s de um Blu Ray ou sinal de TV HD utilizando um receptor de antena via HDMI.</li>\n	<li>\n		Caso o consumidor reclame da qualidade de imagem teste a TV nas condi&ccedil;&otilde;es informadas acima.</li>\n</ul>', 663, 18, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(223, 13, 'Desliga sozinha', '<ul>\n	<li>\n		Durante o funcionamento normal do produto ele se desliga rapidamente (semelhante a um mau contato na tomada), quando isso ocorre &eacute; poss&iacute;vel ouvir o barulho do rele atuando na fonte, por vezes &eacute; poss&iacute;vel observar tamb&eacute;m o LED branco no painel frontal do produto piscar.</li>\n	<li>\n		Este problema pode estar relacionado ao pr&oacute;prio rele <strong><span style="color:#000000;">RL1,</span></strong> a indica&ccedil;&atilde;o &eacute; de troca do mesmo.</li>\n</ul>', 663, 71, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(224, 13, 'Falhas relacionadas a Software!', '<ul>\n	<li>\n		Atualiza&ccedil;&atilde;o de software mais atual,<a href="http://www.p4c.philips.com/cgi-bin/dcbint/cpindex.pl?ctn=32PFL3406D/78&amp;slg=pt&amp;scy=BR" target="_blank"> clique aqui para baixar.</a></li>\n	<li>\n		Detalhes de falhas relacionadas ao software da TV, <a href="http://www.p4c.philips.com/cgi-bin/dcbint/cpcontent.pl?mid=Link_Software&amp;scy=BR&amp;session=20120104115206_187.105.138.234&amp;ctn=32PFL3406D/78&amp;slg=BRP&amp;dct=FUS&amp;did=BRP&amp;reldct=FHI&amp;file=/files/3/32pfl3406d_78/32pfl3406d_78_fhi_brp.pdf#toolbar=0&amp;zoom=100" target="_blank">clique aqui para verificar.</a></li>\n</ul>', 121, 88, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(225, 13, 'Option Bytes para o Produto.', '<ul>\n	<li>\n		Option Bytes para o produto.</li>\n	<li>\n		Para acessar o modo de Servi&ccedil;o, digitar a sequencia<strong><span style="color:#000000;"> (062596 e OK).</span></strong></li>\n</ul>\n<table border="1" cellpadding="1" cellspacing="1" class="tabela" style="width: 500px; ">\n	<tbody>\n		<tr>\n			<td style="text-align: left; ">\n				<strong>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; MODELO</strong></td>\n			<td>\n				<strong>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;OPTION BYTE</strong></td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td>\n				<strong><span style="color:#000000;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; 32PFL3406D/78</span></strong></td>\n			<td>\n				<div>\n					<strong><span style="color:#000000;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; OB1 - 001 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;OB9 - 060&nbsp;</span></strong></div>\n				<div>\n					<strong><span style="color:#000000;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; OB2 - 000 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;OB10 - 071</span></strong></div>\n				<div>\n					<strong><span style="color:#000000;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; OB3 - 195 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;OB11 - 008</span></strong></div>\n				<div>\n					<strong><span style="color:#000000;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; OB4 - 002 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;OB12 - 000</span></strong></div>\n				<div>\n					<strong><span style="color:#000000;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; OB5 - 248 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;OB13 - 064</span></strong></div>\n				<div>\n					<strong><span style="color:#000000;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &n