ww.suportephi.com.br"><span>www.suportephi.com.br</span></a><span> e voc&ecirc; ser&aacute; redirecionado.</span></p>\n											<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify; line-height: 115%;">\n												<span>&nbsp;</span></p>\n											<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify; line-height: 115%;">\n												<span>2 &ndash; <strong>Atualiza&ccedil;&atilde;o de software n&iacute;vel t&eacute;cnico</strong> &ndash; n&atilde;o pode ser realizada pelo consumidor. Fica dispon&iacute;vel no </span><a href="http://www.suportephi.com.br"><span>www.suportephi.com.br</span></a><span>, na se&ccedil;&atilde;o de downloads. Para acessar selecione o modelo do produto. Consulte as informa&ccedil;&otilde;es t&eacute;cnicas para saber mais detalhes de como realizar a atualiza&ccedil;&atilde;o.</span></p>\n										</td>\n									</tr>\n								</tbody>\n							</table>\n						</td>\n					</tr>\n				</tbody>\n			</table>\n		</div>\n		<p align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center; background: #E4E4E6;">\n			<span style="font-size: 9.0pt;">&nbsp;</span></p>\n		<div align="center">\n			<table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" class="MsoNormalTable" style="width: 760px;">\n				<tbody>\n					<tr>\n						<td style="padding: 0cm 0cm 0cm 0cm;">\n							<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 115%;">\n								<span><img alt="" id="_x0000_i1033" src="/tpvision/ckfinder/upload/images/meio_edicao4.png" style="border-top-width: 0px; border-right-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-left-width: 0px; border-top-style: solid; border-right-style: solid; border-bottom-style: solid; border-left-style: solid; width: 760px; height: 15px; " /></span></p>\n						</td>\n					</tr>\n					<tr>\n						<td style="padding: 0cm 0cm 0cm 0cm;">\n							&nbsp;</td>\n					</tr>\n				</tbody>\n			</table>\n		</div>\n		<p align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center; background: #E4E4E6;">\n			<span style="font-size: 9.0pt;">&nbsp;</span></p>\n		<d